      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The words, \"so cried out,\" are not in the most important authorities. It was the business of the centurion to watch all that took place, and to see that the sentence was executed. He must have been standing close under the cress; and there was that in  the whole demeanour of the dying Sufferer, so different from anything that he had ever witnessed before, that it drew from him the involuntary exclamation, ",
        "children": []
